                    </div>
                    <span>I would like to thank the Markway's for writing such a wonderful book.  This book is full of information in helping one deal with social phobia.  This book not only helped me deal with my own issues with social phobia, but it has given me great ideas on how to help my daughter who suffers from Selective Mutism.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">painfully shy</div>
